summary: “When more music comes out, they'll realize that there are dozen of lyrical references and symbolic references, but I try to do...
body:
“When more music comes out, they’ll realize that there are dozen of lyrical references and symbolic references, but I try to do easter eggs in, like, kind of, first round is, like, stuff that they can see that predicts what will happen in a couple of months. There’s also, like, second tier easter eggs which will be revealed upon the album. Then there’s third tier easter eggs which are the most deeply embed easter eggs, which will be like shown on the tour.”

— Taylor Swift talking about the ME! Music Video on Capital Breakfast
